manifest.name: MARBLE RUN
manifest.description: What is MARBLE RUN all about? It's about fun and easy gameplay. It's about creativeness and playfulness. It's about being a part of a big piece, actually a big marble run. Everyone is invited to build a track and add it to the big marble run. By doing so we will all create the longest marble run ever in history. The longer the run gets, the more special bricks will be available allowing us to build even more creative and awesome tracks.Long story short - it's all about building stuff like we all did when we were little kids.

manifest.name: Sky TV Guide
manifest.description:
Find out what's on television now and what's coming up – and record it, wherever you are.

This app contains a seven-day TV listings guide with details of every show on more than 600 channels, including pictures and programme information from the top shows.  It will also tell you other times that the show is on, in case you miss it first time around.

There's also a showcase section featuring the top shows of the day, whether it's a movie premiere, a big sporting clash or the latest must-see drama. Once you've found something you like, the app will also suggest similar shows that you might enjoy too.

The app also features Sky's fantastic Sky+ Record function that allows you to program your Sky+ box away from home, no matter where you are in the world. Once you've picked a show, all you have to do is click the red Sky+ Record button and it will automatically be recorded on your Sky+ box at home. You need never miss a show again.
